quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  3,92,"Bokozwa bolamu te kino bokobimisa ya malamu okati ya maye bolingaka. Mpe na nyoso oyo bobimisaka, ya sôló Allah ayebi yango.",""
  3,93,"Bilei binso bindimamaki kolia mpona bana ya isalayele, longola sé biye isalayele amipekisaki yambo ete torah<sup>1</sup> ekita, loba na bango ete: Boya na torah mpe botanga yango soki ya sôló bozali bato ya bosembo.","[1] Bótala na mikapo 3, 48 na 65."
  3,94,"Mpe oyo akobukela Allah lokuta sima na yango, bango wana bazali babubi.",""
  3,95,"Loba: Allah olobi bosembo ete: Bolanda bosôló ya lingomba ya Ibrâhîm na kati ya bomoko ya Allah, kasi (Ibrâhîm) azalaki te elongo na baye basangisaki (Allah).",""
  3,96,"Ya sôló, ndako ya yambo oyo etiamaki na mokili mpona bato, ezali ndako esantu ya Makkah, oyo epambolama, yango ezali nzela ya bokambi mpona mokili mobimba.",""
  3,97,"Kati na yango bilembo bizali, ndakisa esika eye Ibrâhîm atelemaki. Oyo akokota na kati na yango abatelami. Mpe esengeli na bato kosala hajj pona Allah na ndako wana, mpo na moto oyo azui makoki ya kokoma kuna. Kasi oyo akoboya, ya sôló, Allah atonda bomengo koleka mokili mobimba.",""
  3,98,"Loba: Eh bino baye bozua buku! Mpona nini bozali kopengwa na mikapo mia Allah, mpe Allah azali nzeneneke na maye bozali kosala?",""
  3,99,"Loba: Eh baye bozua buku! Mpona nini bozali kopekisa bandimi na nzela ya (Allah) mpona koluka kotia mbilinga mbilinga mpe bino bozali banzeneneke? Mpe Allah abosani te na maye bozali kosala.",""
  3,100,"Eh bino bandimi! Soki botosi lisanga kati ya baye bazua buku liboso, bakozongisa bino na bopengwi sima ya kondima na bino.",""
